<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0c0e">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/marketing.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    @include('site-nav')

    <main>
      <nav class="shell subnav" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span>
        <a href="/#features">Features</a><span class="sep">/</span>
        <span>Privacy by design</span>
      </nav>

      <section class="feat-hero shell">
        <span class="kicker">Privacy</span>
        <h1>Nothing to hide, because nothing is stored.</h1>
        <p>The whole product is built so there is no personal data in the first place. No cookie, no stored IP, no cross-site profile, and so nothing to consent to.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/dashboard">See a live dashboard</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/#install">Get your script tag</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal section shell" aria-label="Privacy by design preview">
        <div class="code" style="max-width: 680px">
          <div class="code-bar"><span class="chart-cap">The entire payload a visitor sends</span></div>
          <pre class="code-body"><code>{
  "d": "yoursite.com",      // domain
  "p": "/pricing",          // path
  "r": "google.com",        // referrer
  "h": "a3f9c2...",          // hash, rotates every 24h
  "w": 1440                 // viewport width
}
// no cookie, no stored IP, no name, no device id</code></pre>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal section shell" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2 id="how-heading" class="section-title">How it works</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="flow">
          <div class="flow-step">
            <span class="flow-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h3>No identifier is set</h3>
              <p>Nothing is written to the visitor device, so there is no cookie banner to show and nothing to opt out of.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <span class="flow-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Identity is a daily hash</h3>
              <p>A visitor is counted with a hash that rotates every 24 hours, so there is no durable profile to build or breach.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <span class="flow-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h3>The data stays yours</h3>
              <p>Events are written to your own PostgreSQL database, never shared with an ad network or sold on.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal section shell" aria-label="What you get">
        <div class="metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="m-value">No cookies</div>
            <div class="m-label">Nothing stored on the device means no consent prompt and no opt-out to manage.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="m-value">No personal data</div>
            <div class="m-label">No stored IP, no name, and no cross-site identity to leak or hand over.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="m-value">Compliant</div>
            <div class="m-label">GDPR, CCPA, and PECR friendly out of the box, because there is nothing personal to process.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal section shell" aria-labelledby="related-heading">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2 id="related-heading" class="section-title">Pairs well with</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="related">
          <a href="/features/geography">
            <div class="r-name">Geography and devices</div>
            <div class="r-desc">Country without a stored IP or geo lookup.</div>
          </a>
          <a href="/features/real-time">
            <div class="r-name">Real-time visitors</div>
            <div class="r-desc">Live numbers, still without a single cookie.</div>
          </a>
          <a href="/features/metrics">
            <div class="r-name">Pageviews and sessions</div>
            <div class="r-desc">Exact counts from anonymous events.</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal section shell" aria-label="Get started">
        <div class="cta-band">
          <h2>Your numbers. Your visitors' privacy. Both intact.</h2>
          <div class="cta-actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/#install">Get your script tag</a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/dashboard">See a live dashboard</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer shell">
      <div class="footer-bottom" style="border-top: none">
        <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="ghostanalytics home">
          <span class="brand-mark">g</span>
          <span class="brand-name">ghostanalytics</span>
        </a>
        <span>No cookies. No personal data. Powered by Stacks and PostgreSQL.</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
